Mayavi install requirements for python3:

sudo apt-get install python3-pyqt4

sudo apt-get install python3-pip

sudo pip3 install vtk

sudo apt-get install python3-setuptools

sudo apt-get install python3-numpy

sudo apt-get install python3-configobj

Clone mayavi folder on Github: https://github.com/enthought/mayavi

Unzip mayavi-master.zip and inside mayavi-master folfer run:

sudo python3 setup.py install

